values:
So college is goin well right now, despite some of the drama that is still going on, things are deffinatly better then they were b4! I went home for the weekend and realized that Carroll College Parties SUCK ASS!!!! you have to walk like a million miles from the campus, and then when you get to the party theres nobody there, and its just boring and it sucks....GAY!

Saturday was a good day, Worked til 4, then got a new cell phone, and hung out with Tony too....its so nice to be able to be friends with him now, you have no idea how much better that makes me feel and how much that brings up spirits up. Now i really have someone to talk to, and someone to tell me i'm being stupid and someone I know will tell me the truth. Thank you for visitin me in Tuesday, and thank you for the good night on Satuday Tony. It made my life at the moment a whole lot better. Now that things are mended with him...just gotta work on Brandon...HAHAHA NOT!!~ He's a duche bag and can rot in hell for all I care. Him and his new girlfriend can be happy I dont really care too much anymore, I've got better things to worry about, and better things to do with my time rather then worring bout Brandon...he's not really my type anyways, I dont know why I really fell for him anyway..can someone tell me????? Yeah he was nice and all but I dunno it just doenst seem like I shoulda made that choice during the summer...but I'm good right now being single and doin what I want...I'm having a blast....thank god I'm back up at school...this weekend wasnt too great...

As for Chris...things are just weird with that, I hardly talk to him now, and I dunno..i.ts kinda odd..since I'm friends with all the guys on his floor and I'm over there to visit Andrew a lot..well at least last week I was.....Well I'm off to write a paper, just wanted to make a lil update on my life right now, and say a few things that have been on my mind...
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/27960.html

This weekend ROCKED, Friday night...drank a lil bit on my floor with Kim, Mel, Kim's Boyfriend Joel, Courtney, and some other people I dont know...then we went out to someones house, there really wasnt anything goin on there, so we left...and went over to South Scott and hung out with the boys...drank some more..and stuff, Chris got soooooo wasted on Friday night he could hardly stand, it was kinda amuzing, but I felt bad for him, so I tried to take care of him, but he didn't cooperate very well..lol he just wanted to drink more...finally we got him to calm down, and then he slept in my room with Me, on my futon....

Saturday~ kinda a boring day, CHris and I slept til like 2....then I just kinda chilled and picked up the room a bit, and just chilled...Then saturday night...ooo hehe that was great :) I loved every minute of it! Great!!! Went to dinner with Mel and Taylor, we went to Stoners (a pizza place over in the Scotts), Then headed up to the 5th floor to drink with the boys and 2 new girls that I met. We had a lot of fun, at 1st things were slow and we just chilled up there...then after we started to drink, it got better...Mel went out with a friend of hers and I hung out with the guys and Meghan and Angie. We went to a house party but it kinda sucked, there were soooooo many people there and the beer was almost tapped when we got there so we left. We went back up to the 5th Floor and hung out some more, Chris got off work at like 11:15 and started to drink, but by that time I was totally tanked...lol IT was great...but yeah, just hung out for a while, then at like 2 we ordered a Pizza from Papa Johns and we stuck around to eat taht and then Mel and I finally got back to our room at like...umm 3:30...Late night but it was great :) 

Sunday~ my parents came up for a few hours, they took me and Jenny to Applebees, it was delicious! Something other then college food was good! :) Then I just hung out for a while til Mel got back from work, and then we ewnt to studied and did our laundry..so all my clothes are clean :) yay!! That was my day...pretty boring I know!

Today~ umm I dunno, classes were fine, and I did my math homework in Chris's room now he's in class from 4:10-5:10. Then after that I dunno we might go to dinner, but I dunno...I had asked Brandon earlier to go to dinner, but he never got back to me..so I'm not too sure whats goin on..I'm waitin! Then tonight...its a lay low night..Packer Game and such :)
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/27858.html

At first things were rocky, I wasn't all that happy and Brandon was being gay...but NOW..

My Roommate is amazing, I love her to death! She's from Oshkosh so its all good cuz she can introduce me to people and everything. I'm so happy here now. I've met a lot of people thru Mel...and things are goin well :) I've been hangin out A LOT with Mel's friend from high school...his name is Chris, he's a freshman too..Pre Pharmacy...ooo SMART boy :) The guys on his floor are the coolest guys ever! Theres Andrew, Bobby, Paul, Paul, Ryan, Chris, Beau, Joe and others. I've been hangin out over in South Scott a lot lately. The 5th Floor is great! I love it there. I've been off campus a lot lately too, Chris has a car so we go out at night and just hang out. Yesterday I went to his friend Travis's house and we drank a lil bit, and had a good time, then we came back to the dorms and ordered pizza..that Mel and I didn't get to eat. :( O well..I'm goin to lunch with Chris today...He's so cool, we get along so well...it reminds me of hangin out with Tony and the guys...The car talk and everything, I fit in with Chris and his friends REALLY well cuz I talk bout cars with them, and stuff like that...

I played need for speed underground on X-Box the other day in Chris's room, he let me PIMP out the Eclipse...I was so happy :) He said he'll keep it cuz its fuckin awesome! AHH I LOVE IT HERE! At first I wasn't too fond of being up here...but things are SOO  much better now, I've met people in my classes too, they're goin great by the way...I'm just really happy now...

Tonight~~ I guess I'm goin out with Chris and Andrew to hang out in Oshkosh somewhere, then I gotta call Jill and let her know what we're up to, so maybe she'll come hang out with us :) I guess the scotts are pretty cool to live in, the rooms suck but the people on the floors are awesome, and everyone has so much fun..unlike my dorm...I think I've spent more time the last few days in the Scott's not my own room..lol :) mel and i love to hang out with the boys, we all get along so well! lol

I'll write more later, after tonight is done..when I know how fucked I got and then I can talk bout the Oshkosh Parties :) YAY!!!! Have a good day!
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/27432.html

So...it's DEFFINATLY time to get outa here, I need to start over new, I need to get things off my mind, I need to meet new people like all my other friends have done so far. Life SUCKS around here the last few days, and I'm just ready to leave and get on with the next part of my life. 

I know I'm gunna miss my mom and dad, but I really need to get out on my own, and learn how to live without them by my side all the time. Brandon thinks I'm too spoiled..well we'll see how long that lasts!! Without mom and dad by my side I'm really NOT gunna be spoiled anymore. Maybe I'll grow up enough to be able to have a "college" relationship rather then a "high school" one...or so Brandon puts it.

I admit I'm not the most mature person on the planet...and I'm not gunna deny that at all....but I know that the SECOND my parents leave, things will change, and I'm going to be a different person, and it sucks to know that Brandon didnt stick around long enough to see anything happen to me....I guess he'll stick around to be friends, but I dont know how well that will work out..cuz I care bout him so much and its not the easiest thing to just become friends with someone you care about...I love him...i HONESTLY think that I do...and I told him that..but he doesnt feel the same..so ONCE again..I'm always the one to get hurt, and it SUCKS bad! So theres a part of me that wishes I wasn't going to the same school as Brandon so it would be easier to forget..but then theres a part of me thats SO HAPPY that I am...he says he wants to be there for me, and be there for whatever I need. He said..if I'm in a situation I dont want to be in...that I should call him and he'll bail me out, or if somethings wrong..he wants to be the one I call. SO we'll see how well that goes..I dunno...I HAT E LIFE..I REALLY DO!!! I need to get outa here!
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/27271.html

So yeah , I havn't written so much this summer, its been a busy one, and a fun one! I'm so glad I met Brandon and all his friends who are now my friends. It is always hard to say goodbye to friends, last summer it was different, cuz the girls were all still going to be here....but now its for real, cuz I'm the one leaving aswell as everyone else,its differnet cuz I'm not just sayin bye to friends who I'll see in a few days, now I'm sayin bye to people I might not see for months...its hard. I'm starting to think about it more and more and it makes me not want to leave, even tho I know i just need to get away from here...

Melissa~ you're the best friend I have, you've been there thru so much these last 3 years. We both know that Friday is going to be one of the hardest days we'll come to in our friendship, saying goodbye is always the worst thing. If I don't like Oshkosh, don't worry my 1st chioce of schools to transfer to would be La Crosse! I love you! You're the best! I'm going to miss you so much, but I'm glad we have our scrapbook and phones to call eachother whenever we get homesick and miss our friends. I'm going to miss you, but I'm sure we'll stay in touch no matter what! I Love You, you're my best friend!

Heather~ THANK YOU soooo much for being there this summer. All the Tony things, I really need to thank you for helping me, and can't forget u takin care of me at my party! You really didn't have to sit in the bathroom with me! Rascal Flatts was fun, now you've become a fan and we're gunna go see them again!!!! I miss you already, I'm sorry I didn't come see you Thursday night, but I just couldnt do it...I saw you Wednesday so at least I did see you before you left. I can't wait til November!!! I better see you before that tho! I hope you'll drive to Oshkosh sometime to see me and stay with me for a night! WIth no boyfriend, I will be goin out a lot anyways, so I can take you to some parties! :) yay!

Ben, Jenny, Scotty, Lindsay, and Sean~ Thank you for the great summer guys, it was fun! I'm glad I met all of you, and I'm sure we'll keep in touch. Whether I'm with Brandon or not, I'm sure we'll all still talk! Cant wait to see Scotty, Lindsay and Sean in November! :) I'll miss you guys! and Ben and Jenny~ I can see u guys everyday! Ben make sure my room stays clean, I'm gunna need someone to yell at me to clean it! and Jenny~ thanks for being there, you have no idea how much that means to me! I'm sorry I kept u up so late last night, but I'm just glad I had someone there to help me figure things out, you're a great friend :)I hope our theory was correct..but I guess I wont know til I see what happens! I'm glad I met ALL of you!

Brandon~ I'm glad I met you, I'm glad we had something, and if things dont work out, then they dont. I've learned its better to be friends sometimes, and if we're friends its fine with me. I don't want to ruin ur 2nd year of college and I'm not going to let anything ruin my freshman year! I would like to make sure u STUDY tho..cuz u need to get those grades up!!! and Also I still want things to be the same with our friendship but ya know get rid of the physical stuff, its ok to do, it'll be fine! I luv ya, and I hope that things work out with us, but like I said..if they don't then we'll be great friends either way!

So I'm ready to get the hell outa here, I dont leave for another week, but I'm really ready to leave now! I've already been invited to a party at the Football House in Oshkosh, so thats gunna be awesome! A girl that went to my high school is a sophomore up there and she invited me to her birthday bash that her friends are throwing her! So I can't wait for that, and it'll be a good way to meet people!! Countin down the days..ONLY 8 LEFT!!!
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/26958.html

So I havn't written in a while, the last time I wrote I was all about my birthday and how excited I was for that. Well everything went well and my Tattoo is completely healed and lookin good :) But on to why I'm writing tonight...


This summer has been very good so far, I'm happy with all the things I've done and everyone I've seen. My summer has been so great thanks to all my old friends who I've begun to talk to again, the new friends I've met and hung out with, and also the "new friend" who recently walked back into my life. And we can't forget Brandon, he's my newest friend and fellow Oshkosh student (a sophomore), so now I'll have someone to show me around up at school and someone to make sure I stay on track cuz he knows what its like to be a Freshman...Although things have been so good lately, I still miss the GROUP...


The one thing I know I miss more then anything is all the fun times I had last summer. I miss the group so much and I really can't wait til Saturday for Erin and Maren's party to see everyone again...minus Jimmy cuz he's gotta work. For any of you who read this...I miss you guys and before the summer ends we better all hang out one night at Heather's or the bowling alley or something just like we did last summer. There are so many memories that can't be forgotten and I'll never forget the friends I had last summer and the ones I miss so much right now. You guys were the best....and I hope we can all see eachother soon!


In recent news....I had my wisdom teeth out on July 6, that was not cool at all...I was good all day Tuesday and everything I mean I was loopy as my mom would say for a few hours...well most of the day. But I had so many people stop over to see me and that really made my day and made me feel so good. Thank you to everyone who came over and sat with me for a bit...especially Heather, Aly and Jon..it was good to see you guys and thanks for caring enough to stop by, even if it wasn't for long...u heard the Chubby....b...bu...buh....Rabbit story...that was funny hehehe :) and mostly thank you to Melissa...the one who spent the WHOLE day with me...from 2pm til at least midnight. But thanks everyone for caring, I love you guys :)


In the next week..things are gunna be so hectic...wow I don't know how i'm gunna have any time to work. Monday I'm babysitting and going to a movie with Brandon, Tuesday is  WARPED TOUR and thats what I've been waitin for the WHOLE summer!! I can't wait, and Wednesday, Brandon's having his party, and then Friday...SIMPLE PLAN at Waukesha County Fair...amazing! I can't wait for that either! Busy week...Oh I can't wait! until the next time I write...have a great summer everyone, and keep in touch :)
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/26677.html

FINALLY, I am ONE day away from being LEGAL, I'll be legal to go to the pron shop, I can buy cigarettes (eww but just to say I did it I think I will....I gotta find someone to buy them for then...), I'm GETTIN A TATTOO!!! Bright and Early tomorrow morning I'm goin to American Tattoo to get my tattoo...I'm soooo excited :) I can't wait. My birthday is gunna be great, Gettin a tattoo...goin to the porn shop with Heather, goin to the Safe House with the girls..and then either goin to Level 3 or coming home and goin out with Melissa and the Mukwonago crew...it'll be a good day I can't wait :) Yay for being 18! About 10 hours and 15 minutes left to go...yay! I'm countin down..hehe
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/26281.html

So I havn't really updated in a while..things have been so up and down lately. This week although has been pretty wonderful. The whole Tony situation is way outa hand, we both have a lot of growing up to do, me for the most part, but he needs to realize that ignoring the situation isn't going to either change it OR make it any better. We'll never get thru anything if he can't sit down and talk about it. So thats just old news now, this week...

Monday I worked so I didn't really do anything, Tuesday I went to look at tattoo designs with my mom, Greg, and Melissa! and after the tattoo place, I came home and sat around for like an hour when Ryan called..and asked me if I wanted to go with Ice Cream with Melissa, Mitch and Him...so I got to see Melissa TWICE in one day! It was awesome!! Wednesday..Worked...did NOTHING special...

Thursday was a good day, went to track then met up with Britt, Heather, Jon, Aly, Peter, Leslie and of course Mrs. Motisi at American Tattoo so I could watch Heather get her tattoo...I'm kinda nervous about mine, but I'm sooo excited too, heather handled it real well, so I'm not as nervous as I was b4. Then Jon, Aly, Heather and I went to Mamma Mia's and got some pizza...YUMMY it was good :) Then I got my nails done...then after that I met up with Ryan, Mitch, Lando and 2 other guys I don't know at McDonalds...that was interresting...it's not a good idea to throw your cell phone across the restuarant....

Then Tonight..I'm not too sure whats goin on yet...I'm supposed to go to dinner then Ryan is having people at his house so I might stop over there with Melissa, but I gotta get ahold of her 1st....or I'm gunna go out with Heather and I dunno who else...I'll figure it all out when the time comes...gimme a call...

so to wrap it up..I'm pretty happy this week...it's been a good week...and the BEST part of it is gunna be PROM!!! TOMORROW NIGHT! yay! I just hope it doesn't rain for pictures..that would sucK!!
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/26106.html
so umm, I tried to update earlier, but MY STUPID computer froze so I'll have to post what I was gunna say later on, or just some other time...ARG I need a new Computer!
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/25610.html

The best thing and the worst thing happened all in one day...I broke the schools indoor Triple Jump record on Saturday morning, and Tony and I got into a fight about "Us". So that sucked.

Monday~ Went to the mall with Britt...then came home and went to see Starsky and Hutch with Mitch. That was fun to get out and see a friend I havn't seen in like 10 months! I used to talk to him everday and then it just stopped..so it was good a see one of my good friends again!

Tuesday~ O yesterday was so fun!!! Well the morning wasnt...Tony and I hung out for a bit...and basically said GOOD BYE. I dunno when I'll talk to him and I don't know when I'll see him. He agreed that if we hung out with the group that he would deal with the fact that both of us might be there. So that would be ok..but ALONE I dunno when I'll see him alone...so I cried for like 2 hours straight..then went to Track..ran 10, 200's~~ those were such a bitch! lol but i felt like I burned off all the candy I ate on easter! Then after that britt and I went to Swingtime and met up with Angie, Dana, Pilon, Doherty, Josh, and John. That was fun, I learned how to drive a ball!! I've never ONCE held a golf club that wasn't a mini golf club! so Pilon and Doherty tried to teach me..and after a while I kinda caught on..I hit the ball prolly like 75 yards or so..nothing more then that..But it was fuN~ Then dana and I wanted to go in the batting cages...but when I went in the medium hardball one..it broke on me...and I didnt even get a free token..that was gay! After swingtime we went to Rut's house, his dog is the cutest thing I've ever seen...and Ryan's really good at the guitar! So that was fun too..then I had to go get my nails done..and that was the end of my day! 

So yeah last night was fun, and today I'm goin to Mayfair with my mom and Brittney, then Track practice at 3, then work til 9:30....ehh boring day!!
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/25580.html

so lately things have been kinda weird...Tony and i broke up again..but we're talkin now and we're "FRIENDS" i mean we OBVIOUSLY sill like eachother and still care for eachother...i dont really see why we just arent dating cuz we talk the way we used to...havn't said i love you to eachother..but we still talk to eachother with the flirtyness and stuff as we usual do. He came to lunch with me and brittney yesterday...and we hung out last night..and things are just great. I dunno..i just hope that eventually we can realize that our friendship is still there....and then get back together...im not too sure how that will go..but we'll just have to wait and see...i just dunno how things are gunna go right now..He's confused..and I am a little bit too...but i just thought i'd write a bit now..since i havnt written in a while...kinda givin the heads up on whats been goin on in the last week or so...

So...Tony ordered his Intake and his tail lights for his car!! SOO EXCITING!! lol :) He had Yesterday off and he has Friday and Saturday off aswell. yesterday we hung out...Friday after track I'm gunna head to his house..we're gunna take his car for a drive and test what its like b4 the intake..and then he's gunna put the intake in and then we're gunna take it for another drive to see the difference between the stock intake and the new one :) hehe that will be fun..then we're gunna put his lights in...and then last we're gunna go get oil and stuff for my car..and then Saturday..he MIGHT come to watch my track meet..to see me BREAK THE WAUKESAH SOUTH INDOOR TRIPLE JUMP RECORD!!! hehe :) I wanna do it!! i really do!!! I cant wait :) hehe Well gotta get back to class now..write lata bye :)
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/25250.html

So today wasnt that great of a day..I didnt go to school...Tony and I got into a fight on Sunday night for the STUPIDEST reason EVER!! He thought I was mad about something and i wasn't and then we started this rediculous fight...well its all settled now..I spent the day with him today..and things are ok with US..but he hasn't talked to his dad or told his dad that he's even speaking to me right now..so he's afraid his dad is gunna give him shit..but other then that...

I was thinkin today..and yesterday...Yesterday was the start of 4th quarter..and I mentioned the whole senioritis thing settin in...but today..the thought of goin to college set in...I'm actually kinda scared and nervous for that to happen...these last 4 years have gone by SOOOO fast that its just hard to believe that high school is almost over...2 Months and 13 days until graduation...thats just INSANE!!! I can't believe it...

This last quarter is gunna be kinda hard...I'm workin now to break a school track record for Triple Jump indoors..I have 2 weeks to beat it...but at the meet we're goin to this weekend they're not having triple jump..so I have one week to do it...But one thing I'll miss most about high school is track...I'm gunna cry so hard to the banquet...I can see it comin now..my coach says something about each girl on the team...and when he gets to me..he'll say something like "we never thought ashley would be a long jumper until this year...blah blah blah.." and I'll just have tears in my eyes...and Reality has hit...HIGH SCHOOL IS ALMOST OVER...thats kinda sad???......

ok now that I've gotten out what I've been thinkin about ALL day...I'm gunna go watch some TV...later!
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/24896.html

so I havn't written in a while...been busy with Track and everything else...Track has been goin great, I'm long jumping this year notjust triple jumping..YAY i get to do 2 events...lol I'm actually doin pretty welll so far...I havnt done indoor season since freshman year..i've had something wrong that I havnt been able to compete...but this year I'm startin off strong!! So far my best triple jump is 31 feet 4 1/4 inches..and my long jump is 14 feet 10 1/2 inches...so I'm happy and hopefully I'll only get better..maybe I'll have a shot at sectionals this year..that would be the best thing ever :)

I'm in physics..just finished a test...it was hard as hell...but its 4th quarter..I dunno if I care right now...i feel senioritis settin in right about now...I'm surprised I lasted this long...cuz I was all about doin good in classes until Today...which is the start of 4th quarter...I just dont care anymore...its SOOO nice out..and I just want it to be summer NOW!! :) 

After school today Britt and I are goin tanning...cant wait...I need to get a tan! YAY :) Ok well I gotta go now...class is almost over...time to go tanning :) Bye!!
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/24802.html

so today went kinda slow..but now that I'm home I am a lot happier! lol! Tonight is my 1st track meet...its a jv/varsity dual...vs wisconsin lutheran. I dont really feel like competeing today..but I have to have to do somethings to get ready for tomorrows meet! I'm triple jumping and running the open 55 m dash tomorrow in Whitewater and prolly one of the biggest meets I'll ever go to!!! 31 teams tomorrow...I'm gunna get my ass kicked in the 55 by all the fast black girls and others! lol but o well...

SO tonight I wanna go out with everyone...so I think I'll make up some stupid excuse for when I'm done jumpin tonight I gotta go out to eat with my family so I have to leave right away! lol SO then I can go out :) hehe I'm such a brat....o well I wanna hang out with my friends!

But yeah..now I'm gunna go take a nap for about 45 min..then I gotta go up to school for my meet...Wish me luck for tomorrow!!! I'm nervous for that already!! hehe.... :/

Have a nice night everyone, and IF I DONT SEE THE GROUP~ I'll see you all tomorrow night!!! Hopefully I'll show my face tonight! (as Erin once told me) lol :) See You All Later!
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/24389.html

my 18th birthday~ i know its not til May..but I think I wanna get a tattoo!! I've always kinda wanted one..like a lil rose or gymnast or something. But I was always afraid I'd be too much of a chicken to go thru with it cuz I had needles and I dont think I have a high tolerence to pain....although my mom thinks I do..but anyways...I've been lookin for the last few days at what things I'd like..I've found like 2 or 3 really cute ones that I liked! I know they're kinda plain and everyone gets roses, but I LOVE ROSES and you can change the colors when they tattoo you...so I'd make my roses blue not red :) hehe they're cute to go across my lower back!

 

Thats one that I kinda like..I think its cute :)

WHAT DO YOU THINK????????
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/24071.html

Today was kinda boring and SLOW until Physics!! Physics was so great today...this one girl in my class I think her name is Liz...the girls that sit behind me call her "the mom" cuz she dresses like one and acts like one...we always laugh at Liz and stuff cuz she has a crush on Mr. Vick (my teacher) but today was extra funny cuz we realized she wasnt laughing at Mr. Vick's stupid jokes..she was sleeping! So our class being the mean people that we are...just watched her and kinda laughed that she was sleeping..in the FRONT row of the room. Then someone I dunno who...but someone threw a paper airplane almost hit me in the side of the face and TOTALLY missed Liz...then she looked like she was gunna fall outa her chair so we started to laugh and thats when Mr. Vick realized what we were laughing at...then she woke up to the whole class laughing at her..It was really funny cuz she had NO idea and then she just went back to sleep again. I know its mean..but it was really funny tho! I guess you had to be there! :)
http://gymnastgrl4life.livejournal.com/23885.html

so everything is going so well now, tony and I are back together as of Thursday, i tried to play dumb when he was tryin to ask me back out..but that just didnt work. He said "you can tell chris he was right, this did last about a week" and i tried to hard to be like well what lasted a week? but he knew i couldnt do that..so we're ok now, and things are goin great as of now, no fighting or arguing or anything! we're good to go for now :) hehe

Friday~ was a great night, granted i was so worn out and acted like a lazy ass a bowling, but dinner at PF Changs was wonderful as usual, I LOVE IT! Jimmy got a bag of fortune cookies and he was greedy, i had to steal some from him ..but he got mad at me for that...sorry Jimmy! :) Then we went bowling at Lake View Lanes in Pewaukee, it was fun..but I was so beat from the week of track so I kinda seemed a lil lazy until I woke up a bit. It was great to see everyone together again, and it just seems like its summer again :) I love that feeling...and I just want the summer to come once again!

Saturday~ i had track bright and early in the morning...then went out during the day with Tony, he got a new cell phone...well same phone as b4 but its not broken like the other one. So they just swapped out his old phone cuz the chick said that microphone was gunna die...so he didnt care he got a new phone..now it works! :) yay! Then I worked til 9:30, and Tony got pulled over kinda in the dairy queen parking lot..some cop drove by saw his parking lights on and thought he was gunna either rob the place or dealin drugs, or gunna jump all of us when we left..it was weird, but she called his license in and stuff and it came back as suspended and she told me I had to drive his car home that he wasnt aloud to...so then we went thru all the trouble to get one of my cars to his house...it was a long evening, and then finally we made it back to his house and watched the 1st half of the Lord Of the Rings~ Two Towers extended version..til I fell asleep at like 1 am...then went home at like 2...long night!
